⊢ summarize
  given sample-code→code ≡ "(full Python source)"
  yield summary

  ∴ Write an architectural briefing of «sample-code→code» for a new team member.
    For each component:
    (a) Name the pattern it implements.
    (b) Explain what problem that pattern solves — why this choice over alternatives.
    (c) Describe how it composes with the other components.
    (d) Identify extension points for adding new behavior.
