  ⊢= observation ← "v0.2 FILE-SCOPE ⊨? WORKS AS DESIGNED: the file-scope ⊨? on exhaustion: partial-accept(best) was never triggered because ⊢∘ converged within max 5. But it provides a clean fallback: if the prompt couldn't reach score 8 after 5 iterations, the best-scoring version would be accepted. This is the v0.2 clarification that file-scope ⊨? applies to all cells without local ⊨? — previously ambiguous, now spec-compliant."
